{"tid":2517102,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個中、小學校園生涯美好回憶","createTime":"2021-05-05T06:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T18:00:10.000Z","uid":10014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db30366397d87c891d1b89882674223fcada674b","tid":2517102,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"小學六年級唔知有個咩比賽贏左可以全校一齊去海洋公園<br />\n<br />\n點知出發果日黃雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啲miss阿sir contingency plan就叫我地留校一日<br />\n<br />\n有一段時間帶我地成班去職員休息室唱K<br />\n<br />\n果時好興謝檸檬同八神頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我竟然可以同我第一個鐘意對象合唱《一擊即中》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記得驚到仆街出手汗，下手揸枝咪嘅時候話「咁撚濕既」，俾全班笑鳩我鐘意人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但果日算係小學最開心既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1363e130a3f864eb546e32860bcbfcf8fd382fe7","tid":2517102,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"屌 原來有個相同post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由我沉啦"},{"pid":"c07d3c1888a6c9f6ec6c8b636ddfde9401b83f16","tid":2517102,"uid":362865,"like":5,"dislike":0,"sco